<text x="430" y="447" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="9" fill="rgba(15,18,30,0.55)" letter-spacing="1.5">4% OF 72H MINIMUM  ·  ENFORCEMENT EXPOSURE</text>
